{
  "stem": "3666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when you worked with these non-Jewish people, they weren't hateful to you in any way?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean some of them, because you just described some of them were helpful to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right, I don't remember the display of hate within the working quarters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember that, and the rest of the milieu was together with my own people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did the people, the Jewish people, act under those very trying conditions?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember incidents of fights, verbal as well as physical.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was for themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As they say, every man for themselves, because you knew that if you don't do things for yourself, nobody else is going to do it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people were as civil as we should be, but not everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also there is a distinction, I think, and this really worried me all the time-- these class distinctions, which did happen, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even there, and the worst part was when the Hungarian Jews arrived, and again, there was a definite dichotomy between us and them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that, too, I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an unfortunate situation because they took every Hungarian, or maybe Czechoslovakian, or Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took them on the outskirts of Riga, and they slaughtered them, just like [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they didn't even stay at camp, and then we later found out what they did with them, which was just tragic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I I don't know, but in Hungary and in Czechoslovakia, maybe the conditions weren't as harsh as what you lived under.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember resenting anybody, but I do remember that there was some kind of friction.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, I think they resented us, now that I think of it, and it's interesting why.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
